OL,3,CUnion urges Tata to negotiate over
OL,4,CPort Talbot blast furnace closure
OL,5,Cthreats
OL,7,FA steel union has called for Tata
OL,8,FSteel to hold further talks with them
OL,9,Fafter the company told staff that both
OL,10,Fblast furnaces in Port Talbot could
OL,11,Fclose as early as next week.
OL,13,FTata had planned to close one of its
OL,14,Fblast furnaces before the end of June,
OL,15,Fwith the other shutting down by
OL,16,FSeptember, but said it would take
OL,17,Fsteps to cease operations at the Port
OL,18,FTalbot plant earlier than planned
OL,19,Fbecause of safety fears ahead of a
OL,20,Fproposed strike by Unite the union.
