OL,4,CPort Talbot blast furnace closure
OL,5,Cthreats
OL,7,FIn a message to employees on Thursday,
OL,8,FChief Executive Officer, Rajesh Nair
OL,9,Fsaid: "Therefore, we are left with no
OL,10,Falternative but to take preparatory
OL,11,Fsteps to cease operations on both
OL,12,FBlast Furnaces (including the wider
OL,13,Fheavy end assets) and safely isolate
OL,14,Fthem no later than Sunday 7 July 2024."
OL,16,FUnite called the strike in protest at
OL,17,Fthe company's plans to cut thousands
OL,18,Fof jobs by ending traditional
OL,19,Fsteelmaking at the site and moving to
OL,20,Fa greener form of steel production.
